com.ibm.portal.model
Interface ClientListControllerHome

public interface ClientListControllerHome

Home interface for JNDI based lookups for ClientListControllerProvider. Note that this service may be invoked from within portlets. See the following sample on how to obtain a client list model controller:

ClientListController result = null;
final Context ctx = new InitialContext();
final ClientListControllerHome home = (ClientListControllerHome) ctx.lookup(ClientListControllerHome.CLIENT_LIST_CONTROLLER_JNDI_NAME);
if (home != null) {
result = home.getClientListControllerProvider().createClientListController(aClientList);
}

Since:
6.1.0
